tabbrowser-menuitem-close =
    .label = бһ”бһ·бһ‘
# Displayed as a tooltip on container tabs
# Variables:
#   $title (String): the title of the current tab.
#   $containerName (String): the name of the current container.
tabbrowser-container-tab-title = { $title } - { $containerName }

## Confirmation dialog when closing a window with more than one tab open,
## or when quitting when only one window is open.

tabbrowser-confirm-close-tabs-button = бһ”бһ·бһ‘вҖӢбһ•бҹ’бһ‘бһ¶бҹҶбһ„

## Confirmation dialog when opening multiple tabs simultaneously

tabbrowser-confirm-open-multiple-tabs-title = бһўбҹҮбһўбһ¶бһ„вҖӢбһҖбһ¶бһҡвҖӢбһ”бһҫбһҖ
tabbrowser-confirm-open-multiple-tabs-button = бһ”бһҫбһҖвҖӢбһ•бҹ’бһ‘бһ¶бҹҶбһ„

